features: 【Worry-Free Cable Management Solution】： This cable management under desk offers a simple and effective way to manage wires in both home and office settings. The primary function of our cable organizer is to neatly organize cables, reducing the risk of electrical hazards due to disorganized wires, thus protecting children and pets from potential electrical harm.

【Thoughtful Adhesive Design】: With pre-attached adhesive tape, installation complexities are eliminated. Simply choose a smooth surface, peel off the backing film, and apply with ease. The cable management can be removed damage-free, without leaving any residue, ensuring a convenient and harmonious organizing experience. For optimal adhesive longevity, please wait 24 hours after installing the under desk cable management before placing wires.

【Easy-Access Outward-Facing Opening】: Our cable management kit features a unique outward-facing opening that makes inserting and removing cables straightforward, avoiding the difficulties associated with cable placement in traditional desk inward-facing cord organizer for desk.

【Versatile Installation Options】: Whether it’s managing cables under a desk, concealing wires in a corner, or storing cords on a desktop, this cord management can easily meet your needs. Note that adhesive tape of the cable raceway might not stick as well on powdery or uneven surfaces; for best bonding results, install the desk cable management and wait 24 hours before placing wires.

【Quality PVC Material and Flame-Retardant Feature】: Our wire organizer is made with durable PVC material and boasts an excellent flame-retardant design. In the unlikely event of extreme conditions, the material will not produce an open flame but will only char, ensuring a higher level of safety for your home and office environment.

【You Will Get All】: In addition to two 15.7 in wire organizers for cords and five practical cable ties, we promise to provide high-quality customer service. We will respond promptly to any concerns, committed to delivering an exceptional shopping experience and standing by to assist you at any time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for standing desk with thick desktop
reviews.reviewText: I have a standing desk with a 2.5” thick desktop to accommodate it having a drawer. Most cable management devices just don’t fit. This however worked perfectly. Time will tell how good the adhesion is but it feels very secure. I did clean it with rubbing alcohol before adhering. For this setup I have a 12 outlet + 3 usb surge protector and a secondary 10 port usb hub secured with very heavy duty Velcro on the underside of the desk - more outlets than I will ever need. The desk itself also has usb outlets and a charging pad. These cable management strips are secured on the backside of the desk holding all of the excess cables. This keeps everything away from cats who think cables are toys, ensures everything moves smoothly when moving the desk up and down and keeps it neat and tidy. The cable channels are pretty low profile and don’t cause the desk to bump out from the wall. Most of my cables are normal size and because everything is secured up do not put a lot of weight on them. I have power cables for two computers, a printer and various accessories - phone charger, external light and camera, monitor cables etc. it’s important to note that these are not large enough to accommodate any computer charger bricks so have a plan for those. I have one for each computer and they are secured to the desktop above the channels out of the way so they do not put pressure on anything. Overall this works great with this style of desk to keep everything tidy and secure.
